{"tid":1970720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白雲着T-Back潛水慘被叫妓女扯火反擊","createTime":"2020-04-13T10:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T12:06:11.000Z","uid":297241,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0ffe3f4cc0cdb4d695b0a3043d0da784670ac490","tid":1970720,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"白雲着T-Back潛水慘被叫妓女扯火反擊<br />\n<br />\n日前網晒身穿T-back比堅尼潛水短片的35E咪神白雲，昨日自爆被網民辱罵是妓女，即以性感床照反擊，聲言自身清白：「我對愛情和性愛要求都很高！」採取你有你罵，我有我做的態度，更承認多年來深受身材歧視，就連閨蜜也會同樣輕蔑她！<br />\n<br />\n身懷35E超級「胸器」成為咪神多年的白雲，近年轉型為YouTuber常分享旅遊及潛水等短片，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於她常以比堅尼上陣，大騷逼爆身材，加上噱頭多多包括水底飲汽水等，故一直吸引網民追看</span>。日前她上載回顧初學潛水的短片更成為熱話，因片中她穿的是T-back比堅尼，令網民看得目不暇給，她更留言說是首次穿。"},{"pid":"7fb777ffae0e2540eba10f85cc0b258a3a44099b","tid":1970720,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f64e685e864cfb33682ae4757716338c5ae740","tid":1970720,"uid":130693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"10秒.gif"},{"pid":"529aaeaa055c15233b696a1617434ef7994566fa","tid":1970720,"uid":64444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"圖呢？"},{"pid":"8547d6df7a84cdab68256ec05da9b4787276178b","tid":1970720,"uid":89714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"圖都無張就收皮啦"},{"pid":"4aadc0cb2685d8e21a596abd19d1286adf7bd92c","tid":1970720,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"529aaeaa055c15233b696a1617434ef7994566fa","tid":1970720,"uid":64444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"圖呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200413/photo/bkn-20200413033317897-0413_00862_001_03p.jpg?20200413033344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb